% This file tests comments, text/code/eval fragments and constant definitions
This is text
% This is a LaTeX comment
<<<
a : N
a := 0  % and this is an NBM comment!
>>>
more text
<<<     % we can have as many code blocks as we want
b : N
b := a  % identifier reference
>>>
And now we use evaluation to determine {{{a}}} and {{{b}}}.